eu.amidst.core.datastream

Class Attributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.datastream.Attributes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Attribute>

    public class Attributes
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<Attribute>
    This class acts as a container of the Attribute objects of a data set.

    See eu.amidst.core.examples.datastream.DataStreamExample for an example of use.
